snippet.textDisplay:
People need to understand that before passing an opinion listen to the song at least 2-3 times. These songs are a bit longer and a single song has so many different parts you can't just judge all the parts in one single go. Most of the Coke Studio songs grow on you as you listen to them again and again.
I have experienced this myself... In the previous season when Paar Channa De first came out, I thought it was too dull and boring... as I started listening to it again and again I got addicted and found out that it is truly a masterpiece!!
